{"tid":1803140,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【封完星火封bitcoin】","createTime":"2019-12-30T03:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T04:21:20.000Z","uid":322412,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b307522ce6f0f91a6ad6cc21a150475105a8e4b","tid":1803140,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:46:04.000Z","msg":"封完星火封bitcoin： 星火之後 黑警要封殺比特幣同其他電子貨幣！！<br />\n<br />\n有炒開比特幣人托我同大家講 黑警正調查 Tether 公司有無幫被捕手足開户同現金交易紀錄<br />\n<br />\nTether 公司係香港既加密貨幣結算公司 例如有人賣比特幣要換現金 首先要沽出 bitcoin/USDT 呢個品種 咁USDT 就會將美金滙比 Tether 香港USDT acc 之後替大家交收<br />\n<br />\n香港既 USDT acc 由Tether 公司管理 即係香港人加密貨幣資產都係Tether  USDT acc 裡面 或者支那人通過香港炒coin 都係<br />\n<br />\n咩吾係加密貨幣追查吾到身份？ 確實係 但黑警直接郁個金庫 凍結個USDT户口咁揸bitcoin 其他Xcoin既人短期結算吾到 <br />\n<br />\n大家都知果堆coin 比大陸人洗錢用 今次仲易比黑警凍結  請通傳比有揸bitcoin 或其他coin既手足早D做準備<br />\n<br />\n利申： 代人發帖 未玩過bitcoin吾太熟交收程序"},{"pid":"b7db05ace0361a3ac5a4762734cda5a48af859ea","tid":1803140,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/11/10/7jMSV2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F11%2F10%2F7jMSV2.png&h=9c34f3a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a489df271ffa15128ece4feb07949eb115183325","tid":1803140,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7db05ace0361a3ac5a4762734cda5a48af859ea","tid":1803140,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/11/10/7jMSV2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F11%2F10%2F7jMSV2.png&h=9c34f3a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:56:58.000Z","msg":"吾吾"},{"pid":"414bb6b515e95fb1a8c671ab1fc344e739e0e015","tid":1803140,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/11/10/7jMSV2.